{"tid":2130933,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"再度被商戶割蓆 曹永廉籲正義之人團結救港","createTime":"2020-07-29T13:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:43:57.000Z","uid":183844,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe6ceccfa92da0c7fd26abbf9a44410b64d8149","tid":2130933,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">Too Long Didn't Read: 曹永廉又又又又比人割蓆，Bigbigshop又少一間商戶，大家即刻Follow TVB民間團隊支持吓佢地先，跟住拉落去間商戶派心心！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sayno4tvb FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5fafc4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a> Sayno4tvb TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=69ae8b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3m3pdN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3m3pdN.png&h=adf7c46d&s={SIZE}\" /> ====================================== <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4462368/org/d156cf6427d41ae16518caa86345ced6.PNG/y9wVlEZJ8NbWswJQmBA7L4j6Ptj4OqVy5jlBZuY5QWY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4462368%2Forg%2Fd156cf6427d41ae16518caa86345ced6.PNG%2Fy9wVlEZJ8NbWswJQmBA7L4j6Ptj4OqVy5jlBZuY5QWY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b7e30dbd&s={SIZE}\" /></p> 早前<strong><span class=\"red\">曹永廉喺《bigbigshop感謝祭》幫一間海鮮商戶推銷產品</span></strong>，喺正負得負嘅情況下，該間海鮮商戶形象瞬即插水，被2300名網民派嬲抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHTYdcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHTYdcF.png&h=a94d4f97&s={SIZE}\" /> <span class=\"small\">「再嘈下次搵楊明同麥包幫你賣廣告吖拿（設計對白）」</span></p> 今日，<strong><span class=\"red\">呢間海鮮商戶宣佈同曹永廉、bigbigshop割蓆</span></strong>！佢地話只係知大台會拎佢哋產品拍野，但點拍、畀邊個拍就一概不知情，最後大台就搵咗個曾經俾廣告商凌遲割蓆嘅奀星幫佢推銷，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">喔！！原來係大台擺呢間野上枱！</span></strong></span> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BXcjFatgneA4qqoy-ZxfahQbP9o=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XYY4J25Z4EKEQG6VXYW2M6NVNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBXcjFatgneA4qqoy-ZxfahQbP9o%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXYY4J25Z4EKEQG6VXYW2M6NVNA.jpg&h=a56febad&s={SIZE}\" /></p> 呢間海鮮商戶仲話，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">已經從bigbigshop下架</span></span></strong>，遲啲會研究自己整網頁做訂購，真係割得好徹底呀，<strong><span class=\"red\">疫情之下，生意難做，大家快啲有錢出錢，有心派心，好好「懲罰」呢間金爺海鮮啦</span></strong>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金爺海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Funclekam.seafood%2Fposts%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=84c70bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/</a> <strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"xx-large\">派心！派心！派心！</span></span></strong></p> ====================================== <span class=\"pink\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">【點解要幫襯支持？】</span></strong></span> 1. 金爺海鮮之前<strong><span class=\"red\">只係bigbigshop商戶，唔係廣告商</span></strong>，「2020年開始永久抵制」呢個原則並不適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2. 我哋要做一個示範畀其他商戶睇，<strong><span class=\"red\">只要同紅媒網購割蓆，就會得到消費者支持</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"small\">【老馬有火】塔門第三代島民 65歲漁民爸爸拍住女婿上網賣海鮮 <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200601/ZIHK4TGWEQGTZ7CJRBTBWTN6AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200601%2FZIHK4TGWEQGTZ7CJRBTBWTN6AM%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=7329aead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200601%2FZIHK4TGWEQGTZ7CJRBTBWTN6AM%2F&h=64a9c224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200601/ZIHK4TGWEQGTZ7CJRBTBWTN6AM/</a></span> ====================================== <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHugKqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHugKqz.jpg&h=f37c4c06&s={SIZE}\" /> </p> 金爺同奀星割蓆後個零鐘，《文匯報》就出版咗兩篇曹永廉既文章，大概就係話老婆仔女都係加籍既自己點慘點慘，但係無愧於心，佢仲話<strong><span class=\"red\">「其實廣告商與我都是很好關係，他們只擔憂商舖被打砸，我是明白的，累及他們我都於心不忍」</span></strong>，link唔貼啦，都係廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ============================================ 如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5fafc4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a> TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=69ae8b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a> 舊版抵制List: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbadver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbadver&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=0860b93e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/tvbadver</a> 最後都要重申，<span class=\"red\">我地支持自由經濟，我地同意廣告商有賣廣告既自由，但顧客都有選擇買同唔買既自由</span>，我地只會抵制無良商戶，但唔會威脅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbYiswE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbYiswE.jpg&h=d3b9ed92&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVG4nk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVG4nk5.jpg&h=69dd4c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f589e5f433093902bca2a11d5bff264217b3176","tid":2130933,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"報捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a2d2a5ed4a07085bfc49c0895b66186b36410","tid":2130933,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e9ca9f1b3c56521d4a8dc2a76b584f3e2e83181e","tid":2130933,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51edec72c4171aa2f6c195bc3332c3130e1f9819","tid":2130933,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f589e5f433093902bca2a11d5bff264217b3176","tid":2130933,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"報捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"格式亂曬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765ac6589003be3f6a4981db1fbdf6b2b4c7327a","tid":2130933,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:17:45.000Z"